&lt;h2&gt; Citation
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;« I regard writing not as investigation of character but as an exercise in the use of language, and with this I am obsessed. I have no technical psychological interest. It is drama, speech and events that interest me. »&lt;/p&gt;
